      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 44,
      "message": "if possible, I suggest defining simpler path; something like:\n/workflows-management/activate?workflowUuid=uuid&serviceInstanceId=uuid&vnfInstanceId=uuid\n\nNote that:\n - /vid/ is already provided by high-level tomcat\n - /workflows-management/ is defined as WorkflowsController's base mapping\n - /v1/ is not needed, as I see it, as it's an internal API, and client (i.e. our FE) evolves together with no backward versioning.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4379,
        "name": "Ittay Stern",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "ittay.stern@att.com",
        "username": "ittays"
      },
